Text: I got this working. Only a 91 Day period however. Go to Kaspersky's site and download Kaspersky's Internet Security 2012. When it's done installing and such, activate trial mode. Go to enter key, and unplug your ethernet/disable wireless. Enter "T1JVS-NNMBD-K1QTN-SUBP8" and click next. It will tell you it's wrong, and at the bottem there is a browse section. Click it and find the torrent. Open the KIS 2011-2012 and click the first one. You now have 91 days, so plug your internet back in.
my antivirus found traces of malware in it.
Thank you very much and  have a nice day ^^ .
